{"title":"信","authors":["李正峰"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李正峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红厂房的顶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜鹊叫喳喳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女伴们拿来了你的信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢着要看它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你胡写的啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万一被丫头们看去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真教人羞煞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拆开了信封，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见一句话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻盈地飞出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一团白棉花……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好哥哥呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你聪明透啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有妹妹懂得它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片洁白的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像这团棉花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上除了它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺织女工还爱啥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞跑回宿舍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧着白棉花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕下抽出那张报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭紧房门再看它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那双黑眼珠呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞅得我心窝乱嘣?……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照片下印着一行字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下放干部，植棉专家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥在公社种白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情意藏在锄头下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉线长长吐不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹用它织彩霞……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}